-- Putin Says He’s Too Busy Working to Use Twitter, Internet
-- B y   I l y a   A r k h i p o v
-- 2012-02-01T12:10:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-01/putin-says-he-s-too-busy-working-to-use-twitter-internet.html
Prime Minister  Vladimir Putin  said he
doesn’t use the Internet, particularly Twitter or other social
networking tools, because he’s too busy working.  Putin was speaking at a meeting in Moscow today on election
observers, a month before presidential elections.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Arkhipov in Moscow at 
